    "description": "Kawai Akira, a kind-hearted boy, is hit by a runaway truck to save a girl. Near his death, a mysterious fairy appears and tells him that she will reincarnate him into another world as he desires.

He had only one wish for the fairy: to be the best looking man in the world...",
