    "description": "I'm Okamoto Eisuke, an office worker whose hobby is quietly camping in dungeons on the weekends while hiding the fact that I'm actually a top-class adventurer. At work, I'm also a low-level corporate slave constantly targeted by power harassment from my awful department manager, spending my weekdays in misery. During one of my weekend getaways, just as I was about to prepare my usual camp meal, I stumbled upon a scene where a gyaru, Inami Melody, was about to be devoured by an SS-class monster, and I ended up saving her without thinking. It seems the whole thing went viral, and suddenly my name is all over the trending tab...!",
