  {
    "author": "Shu Aihara",
    "cover_url": "https://uploads.mangadex.org/covers/c3f18842-383c-4118-b134-daf31d2889a2/99c2b709-92df-48ec-b8bd-e98f849b1571.jpg.256.jpg",
    "description": "Tenma, who is recognized by everyone as a perfectly handsome man, proposes to Amane, a member of his fan club, on a date, but is rejected.
The reason is "because he's my oshi." Huh? Doesn't "oshi" mean "to like" something?
Unable to accept this, Tenma devises a plan (a charade) to get Amane to notice him.",
    "id": "c3f18842-383c-4118-b134-daf31d2889a2",
