    "description": "Nao, Yuki, Tomo and Rio are four brothers working as maids in their family's maid cafe Cherry Girls. While Nao, Tomo and Rio are perfectly fine with dressing up like girls, Yuki is very reluctant about it, but still goes along with it after his brothers coax him in various ways.",
