    "title": "Peerless Battle Spirit",
    "year": null,
  },
  {
    "author": "Mori Kouji",
    "cover_url": "https://uploads.mangadex.org/covers/e939aa14-37e7-4fd1-9923-ddad014c5c1e/7617fc38-72b8-419d-b979-97e5aa926ffe.jpg.256.jpg",
    "description": "Memorial for Kentaro Miura from the final chapter of 'Berserk'.

Will continue to chapter 1 whenever Mori-san will get to publishing it.",
    "id": "e939aa14-37e7-4fd1-9923-ddad014c5c1e",
