    "description": "Adventurers dive into the dangerous dungeon with the help of the <Grace> granted by transcendental existences called Gods. This is the story that covers the hilarious daily life of such Gods and Goddesses and their <Familia>, who are forced to run around on their whims.",
    "id": "8fab2727-d42f-4a41-b5fa-7ac809ec0f5a",
