    "description": ""Uh…Freya-sama left a letter and has left…"  
  
The members of the Freya Familia all turned at once to look at the messenger. Leaving the shocked first class adventurers aside, the uninhibited Goddess of Beauty leaves on a journey to fulfill her desire!",
    "id": "a8fa03d5-0daf-481f-85f8-c0048174d447",
    "status": "completed",
    "tags": "Monsters, Action, Adventure, Magic, Fantasy, Adaptation",
    "title": "Dungeon ni Deai o Motomeru no wa Machigatteiru Darou ka: Familia Chronicle—Episode Freya",
    "year": 2021,
  },
  {
    "author": "Oomori Fujino",
    "cover_url": "https://uploads.mangadex.org/covers/cf16ea31-d883-4458-8eef-72c9651373b7/5b01f9f1-24d8-4cd5-b225-f4986a00aadc.jpg.256.jpg",
    "description": "This is the Labyrinth City Orario. It possesses the only underground labyrinth in the whole lower world, and thus has prospered from it, coming to be known as the "Center of the World." Ryuu Lion, under the owner Mia Grand, worked daily at the pub Hostess of Fertility alongside her coworkers Syr Flova, Arnya Fromel, Chloe Rollo, and Lunoire Faust. One day, a pair of Humans' voices shatters the peace of the store… This is a fairy tale that won't be written down, the Story of Lion!",
    "id": "cf16ea31-d883-4458-8eef-72c9651373b7",
    "status": "completed",
    "tags": "Monsters, Action, Psychological, Comedy, Survival, Martial Arts, Adventure, Crossdressing, Magic, Drama, Fantasy, Monster Girls, Slice of Life, Adaptation",
    "title": "Dungeon ni Deai o Motomeru no wa Machigatteiru Darou ka: Familia Chronicle—Episode Ryuu",
    "year": 2017,
  },
  {
    "author": "Oomori Fujino",
