  {
    "author": "Kawai Aporo",
    "cover_url": "https://uploads.mangadex.org/covers/c42a0974-366a-4349-bcca-25b539769df1/ebc50636-4749-4869-a967-410356195179.jpg.256.jpg",
    "description": "There’s nothing worse than having the guy you’ve secretly crushed on for ten years say you’re like his mom. When Natsume Mishima is given a chance to be in a fake relationship with Chikage, the hottest guy in her class to make her crush Yuuki jealous, she takes it -- even though she hates lying. Will this web of lies get her the guy she wants?",
    "id": "c42a0974-366a-4349-bcca-25b539769df1",
    "status": "completed",
    "tags": "Long Strip, Romance, Web Comic, Full Color",
    "title": "There’s Love Hidden in Lies",
    "year": 2021,
  },
  {
    "author": "Kataihuafoo",
    "cover_url": "https://uploads.mangadex.org/covers/e97d5eed-e3ef-427b-9d9a-aae4c28302c4/4f89ba7b-51ee-415c-ab4b-a9f67b45f7d3.jpg.256.jpg",
    "description": "Just an ordinary girl who had just started her high school life, but she never thought that something would happen and she ended up getting involved with the most senior naughty guy in school. Plus she was asked to be her boyfriend. And what will his life be like after this?",
    "id": "e97d5eed-e3ef-427b-9d9a-aae4c28302c4",
    "status": "ongoing",
    "tags": "Long Strip, Romance, Drama, School Life, Web Comic, Full Color",
